<section id="features" class="section band-paper">
  <div class="usb-head reveal">
    <div class="eyebrow-mono on-paper" style="justify-content:center">The difference</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">Stop being the USB cable between AI and your tools.</h2>
    <p class="sec-lead">ChatGPT gives you text. You copy it. You paste it into Gmail. You open QuickBooks. You paste again. You are the integration. Houston plugs in directly.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="usb-grid reveal reveal-d1">
    <div class="usb-card">
      <span class="usb-badge">ChatGPT</span>
      <h3 aria-label="Follow up with stale leads, the ChatGPT way">Follow up with stale leads</h3>
      <div class="usb-steps">
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">1</span><p>Open HubSpot. Find stale leads. Copy their info.</p></div>
        <div class="usb-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">2</span><p>Paste into ChatGPT. Explain context. Get a draft.</p></div>
        <div class="usb-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">3</span><p>Copy the draft. Open Gmail. Paste. Personalize. Send.</p></div>
        <div class="usb-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">4</span><p>Go back to HubSpot. Log the activity. Update the status.</p></div>
        <div class="usb-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">5</span><p>Repeat for each lead. 12 leads means 60 tabs.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="usb-card is-houston">
      <span class="usb-badge">Houston</span>
      <h3 aria-label="Follow up with stale leads, the Houston way">Follow up with stale leads</h3>
      <div class="usb-steps">
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">1</span><p>Tell your agent: "Follow up with stale leads."</p></div>
        <div class="usb-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">2</span><p>It reads HubSpot, writes 12 personalized emails, sends from Gmail, and logs everything.</p></div>
        <div class="usb-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="usb-step"><span class="n">3</span><p>Done. You review the results.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
